CatDescriptText: A detective wearing a three piece suit and carrying a fedora points to wooden basket filled with trash in an old fashioned kitchen.  The kitchen has a freestanding wood or coal-burning stove with a large stove pipe.  It stands in front of a bricked-up fireplace with a mantelpiece.  Brushes and an oil or kerosene lamp stand on top of the mantel and pots and pans hang below.
TitMainTitle: Man, possibly detective, wearing three piece Glenn plaid suit standing in room with wood burning stove, pointing to bushel basket filled with rags and metal hook
